      "type": "teach",
      "title": "Meet ian",
      "body": "One more ligature rounds out the family: ian, 𐑾 — a quick glide from “i” into “a”. It hides in some very common words: real is 𐑮𐑾𐑤, really 𐑮𐑾𐑤𐑦, and idea is 𐑲𐑛𐑾.",
